%% Жизненный цикл сделки (deal pipeline)
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Lead: создан лид

    Lead --> Qualified: квалифицирован
    Lead --> Lost: дисквалифицирован

    Qualified --> ProposalSent: отправлено КП
    Qualified --> Lost

    ProposalSent --> Negotiation: переговоры
    ProposalSent --> Lost

    Negotiation --> ContractDrafted: проект договора
    Negotiation --> Lost

    ContractDrafted --> ContractSigned: подписан
    ContractDrafted --> Lost

    ContractSigned --> Reserved: товар зарезервирован
    Reserved --> Shipped: отгрузка
    Shipped --> Invoiced: счёт выставлен
    Invoiced --> Paid: оплата получена

    Paid --> Won
    Won --> [*]
    Lost --> [*]

    note right of Reserved
        stock_movements: op=reserve
    end note
    note right of Shipped
        stock_movements: op=out
    end note
    note right of Invoiced
        invoices.status = sent
    end note
    note right of Paid
        payments.direction = in
    end note
